sentence: list all flights leaving on thursday morning from new york city to montreal
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', v0.departure_time, '"'||v1.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.day_name||'"', v2.year, v2.month_number,
 v2.day_number, '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.city_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_name||'"' FROM flight v0,
 days v1, date_day v2, airport_service v3, city v4,
 airport_service v5, city v6 
WHERE ((v0.departure_time BETWEEN  0 
AND  1200) AND (((v0.flight_days = ANY v1.days_code) 
AND ((v1.day_name = ANY v2.day_name) AND (((v2.year =  1993) 
AND (v2.month_number =  6)) AND (v2.day_number =  3)))) 
AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) AND ((v0.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) 
AND (v6.city_name = 'MONTREAL'))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME BETWEEN 0 AND 1200 AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME IN ( SELECT DATE_DAY.DAY_NAME FROM DATE_DAY WHERE DATE_DAY.YEAR = 1993 AND DATE_DAY.MONTH_NUMBER = 6 AND DATE_DAY.DAY_NUMBER = 3 ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NEW YORK ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MONTREAL ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
